sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/Platform
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>8080/TCP HTTP Metrics
    participant Registry as Container Registry<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant RayHead as Ray Head Pod<br/>6379/TCP GCS<br/>8265/TCP Dashboard
    participant RayWorker as Ray Worker Pod
    participant Redis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP Optional TLS
    participant S3 as S3/GCS Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>9090/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,K8sAPI: Flow 1: Ray Cluster Creation
    User->>K8sAPI: POST RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch Notification<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>Auth: ServiceAccount Token
    RayHead->>Registry: Pull Ray Image<br/>Auth: Pull Secret
    RayWorker->>Registry: Pull Ray Image<br/>Auth: Pull Secret
    RayWorker->>RayHead: Connect to GCS<br/>6379/TCP<br/>Auth: Redis Password

    Note over User,S3: Flow 2: Ray Job Submission (via APIServer)
    User->>K8sAPI: POST /apis/v1/namespaces/{ns}/jobs<br/>8887/TCP gRPC<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
    K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch RayJob
    Operator->>RayHead: Submit Job<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Execute Tasks<br/>6379/TCP GCS

    Note over User,S3: Flow 3: Ray Serve Traffic
    User->>K8sAPI: HTTPS Request<br/>443/TCP TLS 1.2+
    K8sAPI->>RayHead: Forward to Serve<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    RayHead->>RayWorker: Serve Request<br/>8000/TCP HTTP
    RayWorker-->>RayHead: Response
    RayHead-->>K8sAPI: HTTP Response
    K8sAPI-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over Operator,S3: Flow 4: Monitoring & Metrics
    Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape Metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    Prometheus->>RayHead: Scrape Metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over RayHead,S3: Flow 5: GCS Fault Tolerance
    RayHead->>Redis: Store GCS State<br/>6379/TCP<br/>Auth: Redis Password
    RayHead->>S3: Store Checkpoints<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>Auth: AWS IAM/GCP SA
